# SDD Workflow Rules

Before implementation, read:

1. docs/sdd_development_standard.md
2. target spec.md
3. target plan.md
4. target tasks.md
5. target acceptance.md

Implement only tasks explicitly listed in tasks.md.
Do not expand feature scope.
Preserve original file safety rules.
Keep CLI operations idempotent.
